IF EXISTS

     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]

2022-07-04 22:28:10.765 +03:00 [Debug] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=["@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)"], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY [p].[Rating] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth]

) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY [p].[Rating] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Rating] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"

    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth]

    ORDER BY [p].[Rating] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]

LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth], CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth], CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth], CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth], CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth], CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth], CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY [p].[Rating] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Rating] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth], CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]

LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth], CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY [p].[Rating] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Rating] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[Approved], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CountInStorage], [t].[Description], [t].[Model], [t].[PackageId], [t].[PreviewImage], [t].[Rating], [t].[RetailPrice], [t].[Series], [t].[Title], [t].[Type], [t].[VendorCode], [t].[WarrantyMonth], [b].[Id], [b].[Country], [b].[Description], [b].[Name], [c].[Id], [c].[ParentCategoryId], [c].[PreviewImage], [c].[Title], [p0].[Id], [p0].[CountInPackage], [p0].[Volume], [p0].[Weight], [i].[Id], [i].[FilePath], [i].[ProductId], [p1].[Id], [p1].[ProductId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[Value], [c0].[Id], [c0].[Date], [c0].[DislikesTotal], [c0].[IsRemoved], [c0].[LikesTotal], [c0].[ParentId], [c0].[ProductId], [c0].[Raiting], [c0].[Text], [c0].[UserId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth], CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth], CASE
        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END AS [c]

        WHEN [p].[Id] > @__id_0 THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
        ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
    END DESC
) AS [t]

INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]

LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[c] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_0) [p].[Id], [p].[Approved], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[CountInStorage], [p].[Description], [p].[Model], [p].[PackageId], [p].[PreviewImage], [p].[Rating], [p].[RetailPrice], [p].[Series], [p].[Title], [p].[Type], [p].[VendorCode], [p].[WarrantyMonth]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY [p].[Rating] DESC
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN [Brand] AS [b] ON [t].[BrandId] = [b].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [t].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Packages] AS [p0] ON [t].[PackageId] = [p0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[Id] = [i].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductCharacteristics] AS [p1] ON [t].[Id] = [p1].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Comments] AS [c0] ON [t].[Id] = [c0].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Rating] DESC, [t].[Id], [b].[Id], [c].[Id], [i].[Id], [p1].[Id], [c0].[Id]"
